''Perl'' code:

```perl
package Name;
my $singleton;

BEGIN {
    $singleton = {
        attribute => 'value',
        another   => 'something',
    };
    bless $singleton, "Name";
}

sub new {
    my $class = shift;
    return $singleton;
}
```

